<i>Information, it's an era</i>
<i>where it travels in a second</i>

00:00:26.250 --> 00:00:28.520
<i>But you don't know what</i>
<i>choice you should take</i>

00:00:28.520 --> 00:00:30.090
<i>"Money can't buy my love"?</i>

